{
  "stem": "17.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So pretend that everything is-- you are very familiar with, and just go with other people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "So that was the end of our old identity, our old lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was a beginning of a new chapter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was clean, more comfortable, but lonely living among strangers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were friendly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were dangerous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Henry got a job from a friend, Armenian friend, that owned shoe factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He gave him a job, because we didn't have money anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't have any money to support ourselves, to pay the rent and food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was trying to stay as much  home as possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sophie went to work in this small grocery family shop and mangle they have, you know, where they press the linens.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we tried to have as little contact as possible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very lonely life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We knew we lost all families and friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We left ghetto behind and all the suffering people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in April '43, that was the Warsaw Ghetto Uprising.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw the fires, the flames, the smell from, from our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't show any emotion towards the, the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But Henry went to the wall, and he said Kaddish in the wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was as much as, as he could do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were crying at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was nothing, that was the end of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's how we survive on these assumed names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There also was in '44, that was Warsaw Ghetto Uprise-- excuse me, not ghetto-- Warsaw Uprising.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So the Poles fought-- tried to fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Russian led them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They stop in by Vistula.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they led them for six weeks, that was the fight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were also in the middle of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
